DataElement.preferredName: Diagnosis Performed Observation Outcome Report Date and Time ISO21090.TS.DATETIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The identification of a disease or illness by examining the signs and symptoms. The date (and time) on which the result is reported.

DataElementConcept.preferredName: Diagnosis Performed Observation Outcome Report Date and Time
DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: The investigation, analysis and recognition of the presence and nature of disease, condition, or injury from expressed signs and symptoms; also, the scientific determination of any kind; the concise results of such an investigation.:Executed and carried through to completion.:Watching something and taking note of what happens.:The result of an action._A short textual account; having provided a short account.:An expression of both date and time that an event has happened or will happen.
